description: She was so fucking hot in her early 20s, I'm sure she was attractive afterward, but at some point, she stopped being able to run, and she was less active during sex, and that listlessness, from when stylistic death becomes actual death overtook her. Later on in life, when she's in her sixties, you can get her to laugh -- like the old times. Her toothless wheeze will bring a moment of joy into her dreary existence...
name: Based Coraline
